SKILLS (Player Command)
=======================

Usage: skills

Display your character's skill levels and available skills.

The display shows:
  - Your current skills with progress bars and numeric values
  - Basic skills (available to everyone)
  - Guild skills (unlocked by joining guilds)

Skills improve through use:
  - Combat skills improve when you fight
  - Magic skills improve when you cast spells
  - Higher skills are harder to improve (logarithmic curve)

Example output:
  sword           [========            ] 40
  unarmed         [====                ] 20
  dodge           [==                  ] 10

See also: score, attack, cast
